    alpha_s predicted (dimensionless)      0.00082756037156
    alpha_s measured (dimensionless)       0.118

    Relative miss (%%)                     99.298677651

  Measured: alpha_s = 0.1180 +/- 0.0009
  1-sigma range: [0.1171, 0.1189]
  3-sigma range: [0.1153, 0.1207]
  Predicted: 0.00082756
  Within 1-sigma: False
  Within 3-sigma: False

SECTION 3: CONNECTION TO DELTA
----------------------------------------------------------------------

  The alpha_s prediction is the INVERSE of the Delta test.
  In the Delta test: measured alpha_s runs to M_GUT, misses.
  Here: unification FORCES alpha_3 = alpha_GUT, then runs down.
  The prediction misses the measured alpha_s by the same
  amount that Delta measures at M_GUT.

    Delta(1/alpha_3) at M_GUT (dimensionless) 627.49390657

    delta(1/alpha_3) at M_Z (dimensionless) 1199.8964796
    delta(alpha_s) = -alpha_s^2 * delta(1/alpha_s) (dimensionless) -16.707358582

